data.title: 26225 Pine Street, Beaver Island Property Listing: MLS® #474423
data.meta_description: Located on Back Beach, this year-round cottage is in town, but also private, with 102' feet of Lake Michigan shore. Gather on the deck, or around the cozy fireplace, depending on the season. The pole barn could be converted into a guest house for additional family and friends. The walkout basement is partially finished. This home was built by the current owners who are now ready to pass it on to the next family to enjoy!
